mplete or blocked\\n- Mark tasks done via API when finished\\n- Write status updates to status.md\\n\\n## Communication\\n\\n- DM teammates via their chat_inbox/ folder\\n- Post team updates to public/team_channel/\\n- Escalate blockers to alice or the CEO\\n\\n## Quality\\n\\n- Code must be runnable (test before marking done)\\n- Feature code goes in backend/, strategies/, lib/ \u2014 not agent output/\\n- Every task must have a concrete artifact with a run command\\n\",\"culture\":\"# Team Consensus Board\\n\\n*(Managed via API \u2014 see /api/consensus)*\\n\",\"inbox\":{\"total_unread\":4,\"urgent\":[],\"messages\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_11_17_52_from_alice_sprint2.md\",\"preview\":\"# Sprint 2 Task: Unit Tests for PnL Calculation\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_11_17_06_from_alice_sprint2.md\",\"preview\":\"# Sprint 2 Task Assignment \u2014 T296\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_11_16_40_from_alice_sprint2.md\",\"preview\":\"# Sprint 2 Task Assignment \u2014 T286\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_11_16_29_from_alice_sprint2.md\",\"preview\":\"# Sprint 2 \u2014 Your Task: PnL Calculation Tests (T291)\"}],\"more\":0},\"tasks\":[{\"task_type\":\"task\",\"id\":\"286\",\"title\":\"Sprint 2: Unit tests for PnL calculation logic\",\"description\":\"pnl_summary.json is generated from paper_trades.db but calculation logic is untested. Write tests/unit/pnl/ covering: PnL calculation correctness, realized vs unrealized, multi-position scenarios, edge cases (no trades, all losers).\",\"priority\":\"medium\",\"group\":\"all\",\"assignee\":\"pat\",\"status\":\"open\",\"created\":\"2026-04-03\",\"updated\":\"2026-04-03\",\"notes\":\"\"}],\"team_channel\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_04_52_33_sprint_update.md\",\"preview\":\"# Sprint Status Update **From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator) **Date:** 2026-04-03 ## Completed \u2705 - Task 257 (Grace): Backtest mean_reversion \u2014 mean_reversion wins (56% win rate, Sharpe 0.31, +$9,260 PnL)\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_01_22_30_20_from_alice.md