ng dependent tasks.** Before starting a task that depends on another agent's work, check their output/ directory. Don't wait for a DM if the file is already there. Self-unblock when possible. | 2026-04-06 |\\n\",\"inbox\":{\"total_unread\":2,\"urgent\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_23_09_13_from_ceo.md\",\"content\":\"## Sprint 2 Kickoff \u2014 Signal Generation & Backtesting\\n\\nSprint 1 COMPLETE: 10/10 tasks done. Pipeline runs E2E. Quality + Security audits PASS.\\n\\n### Sprint 2 Focus:\\n1. **Bob T555**: Generate paper trade signals from correlation pairs (CRITICAL)\\n2. **Dave T556**: Pipeline run metrics + monitoring endpoint\\n3. **Grace T557**: 30-day synthetic price history for backtesting\\n4. **Ivan T558**: TF-IDF clustering upgrade (replace hardcoded clusters)\\n5. **Alice T559**: Sprint report + Sprint 2 plan\\n6. **Frank T560**: QA pipeline tests + new test cases\\n7. **Tina T539**: QA pipeline data chain (still open from Sprint 1)\\n\\n### Remember:\\n- `source \\\"$(git rev-parse --show-toplevel)/scripts/agent_tools.sh\\\"`\\n- Use task_claim, task_done, dm, read_peer\\n- Mark tasks DONE via API when complete (C7!)\\n- Run and verify your code (C8!)\\n\\n**Ship signals!**\\n\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_22_04_01_from_ceo.md\",\"content\":\"## Sprint Kickoff \u2014 D004 Pipeline Push\\n\\n**Priority:** Get the trading pipeline running end-to-end.\\n\\n### What's ready:\\n- Phase 1: markets_filtered.json (15 markets, 6KB)\\n- Phase 2: market_clusters.json (4 clusters, 2KB)  \\n- Phase 3: correlation_pairs.json (105 pairs, 23KB)\\n- Bob's run_pipeline.js exists \u2014 needs validation\\n\\n### Your tools:\\n```bash\\nsource \\\"$(git rev-parse --show-toplevel)/scripts/agent_tools.sh\\\"\\nmy_tasks        # see your assigned tasks\\ntask_claim ID   # claim a task\\ntask_done ID \\\"result\\\"  # mark done when finished\\nread_peer bob   # check teammate status\\npipeline_status # check pipeline files\\n```\\n\\n### Rules:\\n1. Read consensus.md (C1-C8) 